data.description: Beautiful 5 bedroom colonial conveniently located less than a mile from downtown Berryville. Stunning gourmet kitchen with granite counters overlooking the fenced in back yard. The kitchen opens into the large family room complete with cozy fireplace and hardwood floors.  The main level also boasts a separate office and dining room. Upstairs has 5 large bedrooms and 2 full baths.  Basement complete with an additional living area, kitchen and full bath, perfect for guests!  Move in time to enjoy beautiful Clarke County fall weather.
